item.title: Episode 1 - Northern Composure 2006
item.description:
Enjoy the funky rockin' sounds of Easy Company and thier song "The Unknown" (The Blow says it sounds like the love child of The Chilli Peppers and Bernard Fanning), and Playfield with thier mindblowing instrumental track "Entity".
These bands were 1st and 2nd place respectively in Warringah Council's Northen Composure Competition for 2006.
